text: Ornäs BK is a soccer club in Ornäs in Sweden. In was established in 1982. The women's team played in the Swedish top division in 1999. The women's soccer section was inactive for a while during the first decade of the 2000's. The women's soccer was then restarted. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:1982 establishments in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs
